1) Choose either the simple or the complex test program and link it to
   rnd.f90:

   ln -fs rnd.f90-simple  rnd.f90
   ln -fs rnd.f90-complex rnd.f90
   ln -fs rnd.f90-mecca   rnd.f90    (creates mcexp_seed.txt for mecca)

2) Compile:

   gmake

3) Run the program:

   ./rnd.exe 

4) For the output of rnd.f90-complex, plot results with rnd.jnl
